</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-250_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-251_"><b>Invest in Leadership Development</b> - Equip leaders with the skills to manage, inspire, and support their teams effectively.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-253_"><b>Prioritise Professional Development</b> - Create structured pathways for all staff members' continuous learning and career progression.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-255_"><b>Promote Staff Well-being</b> - Implement programs and policies that support staff health and well-being, recognising the demanding nature of healthcare work.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-257_"><b>Encourage Staff Participation</b> - Involve staff in decision-making processes, particularly those affecting their work and patient care.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-259_"><b>Measure and Reward Performance</b> - Establish clear performance metrics and recognise and reward staff contributions to quality improvement and patient care excellence.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-261_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-262_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-263_">The path forward
